<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>凡音 · DevOps 学习记录</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    body{font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;margin:0;background:#0b1220;color:#e6eaf2}
    .wrap{max-width:860px;margin:48px auto;padding:0 16px}
    header{margin-bottom:24px}
    h1{font-size:28px;margin:0 0 8px}
    p{line-height:1.7;margin:6px 0}
    .card{background:#121a2b;border:1px solid #22304a;border-radius:12px;padding:18px;margin:14px 0}
    a{color:#7fb3ff;text-decoration:none} a:hover{text-decoration:underline}
    code{background:#101826;border:1px solid #1d2a42;border-radius:6px;padding:2px 6px}
    footer{opacity:.7;margin-top:28px;font-size:14px}

    /* 下面是新增：让卡片标题行更像“模块头” */
    .cardHead{display:flex;align-items:baseline;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}
    .cardHead h2{margin:0}
    .subtle{opacity:.8;font-size:14px}
    .iframeWrap{margin-top:10px;border:1px solid #22304a;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;background:#0b1220}
    iframe{display:block;width:100%;height:460px;border:0;background:#0b1220}
    @media (max-width:520px){
      iframe{height:520px;}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <header>
      <h1>凡音 · 个人服务器</h1>
      <p>目标：把 DevOps 学习变成可访问、可维护的线上资产。</p>
    </header>

    <section class="card">
      <div class="cardHead">
        <h2>最近在做</h2>
      </div>
      <ul>
        <li>服务器初始化、UFW、防火墙基线（22/80）</li>
        <li>Nginx 部署静态站点与日志观察</li>
        <li>本地 → 远程的简易部署链路（scp + reload）</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <div class="cardHead">
        <h2>项目链接</h2>
      </div>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/toph312" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub · toph312</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" aria-disabled="true">日志分析（nginx_log_analyser）</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" aria-disabled="true">系统指标采集（server_performance_stats）</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p>注：上面两个仓库链接等你整理好再替换。</p>
    </section>

    <!-- 新增：日历热力图 -->
    <section class="card">
      <div class="cardHead">
        <h2>每日记录 · 日历热力图</h2>
        <div class="subtle">
          <a href="/calendar/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">新窗口打开</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="subtle">说明：字符数热力图</p>
      <div class="iframeWrap">
        <iframe src="/calendar/" loading="lazy" title="Daily Char Heatmap"></iframe>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <div class="cardHead">
        <h2>部署信息（自动化占位）</h2>
      </div>
      <p>最近部署时间：<code><!-- 将来由脚本写入时间戳 --></code></p>
    </section>

    <footer>© <span id="y"></span> FanYin</footer>
  </div>
  <script>document.getElementById('y').textContent=new Date().getFullYear()</script>
</body>
</html>